# Shader sources are byte-compared against in-repo generators (e.g. the Bisqwit
# WGSL drift test `shared_bisqwit_wgsl_matches_generator`). Force LF on every
# platform so a Windows autocrlf checkout can't turn the committed file into CRLF
# and break that strict equality. WGSL/GLSL line endings are not semantic.
*.wgsl text eol=lf
*.glsl text eol=lf
